TCPDF-main/CHANGELOG.TXT:359:	- Bug item #948 "bottom line of rowspan cell not work correctly" was fixed.
TCPDF-main/CHANGELOG.TXT:579:	- TCPDF_FILTERS class now throws an exception in case of error.
TCPDF-main/CHANGELOG.TXT:580:	- TCPDF_PARSER class now throws an exception in case of error unless you define the constant K_TCPDF_PARSER_THROW_EXCEPTION_ERROR to false.
TCPDF-main/CHANGELOG.TXT:713:	- Error() method was extended to throw new Exception if PHP > 5.
TCPDF-main/CHANGELOG.TXT:974:	- Deafult HTTP headers were changed to avoid browser caching.
TCPDF-main/CHANGELOG.TXT:1209:	- Bug #3288763 "HTML-Table: non-breaking table rows: Bug" was fixed.
TCPDF-main/CHANGELOG.TXT:1725:	- The columns widths of HTML tables are now inherited from the first row.
TCPDF-main/CHANGELOG.TXT:2009:	- Bug item #2918545 "Display problem of the first row of a table with larger font" was fixed.
TCPDF-main/CHANGELOG.TXT:2010:	- A Bug relative to table rowspan mode was fixed.
TCPDF-main/CHANGELOG.TXT:2074:	- Support for the HTML "nobr" attribute was added to avoid splitting a table or a table row on two pages (i.e.: <tr nobr="true">...</tr>).
TCPDF-main/CHANGELOG.TXT:2111:	- Bug item #2848892 "writeHTML + table: Gaps between rows" was fixed.
TCPDF-main/CHANGELOG.TXT:2115:	- The Polygon() and Arrow() methods were fixed and improved (see example n. 12).
TCPDF-main/CHANGELOG.TXT:2171:	- Method Arrow() was added to print graphic arrows (example 12 was updated).
TCPDF-main/CHANGELOG.TXT:2307:	- Bug #2717436 "writeHTML rowspan problem (continued)" was fixed.
TCPDF-main/CHANGELOG.TXT:2317:	- The support for rowspan/colspan on HTML tables was improved (see example n. 48).
TCPDF-main/CHANGELOG.TXT:2326:	- thead tag is now supported on HTML tables (header rows are repeated after page breaks).
TCPDF-main/CHANGELOG.TXT:2542:	- A bug relative to rowspanned cells was fixed.
TCPDF-main/CHANGELOG.TXT:2583:	- rowspan mode for HTML table cells was improved and fixed.
TCPDF-main/CHANGELOG.TXT:2597:	- Bug item #2185399 was fixed (rowspan and page break).
TCPDF-main/CHANGELOG.TXT:2602:	- Bug item #2184525 was fixed (rowspan on HTML cell).
TCPDF-main/CHANGELOG.TXT:2767:	- HTML rowspan bug was fixed.
